<div id="pf43fc" class="pf w4f h2fe" data-page-no="43fc"><div class="pc pc43fc w4f h2fe"><div class="t m154 x4c h33 y2f6b ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 9 May 27 to June 2 </div><div class="t m1189 x15 h33 y243d ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;When the day of Pentecost was </div><div class="t m1e0e x0 h33 y238f ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fully come, they were all with one </div><div class="t m622 xb7 h33 y44e ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accord in one place. And suddenly </div><div class="t me86 xb7 h33 yd18 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">there came a sound from heaven as of </div><div class="t m106c xb7 h33 y119 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a rushing mighty wind, and it filled </div><div class="t m170b xb7 h33 yf16 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all the house where they were sitting. </div><div class="t m1214 xb7 h33 y2b0 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">And there appeared unto them cloven </div><div class="t mbcc xb7 h33 yd4f ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tongues like as of fire, and it sat </div><div class="t m1abe xb7 h33 y348 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">upon each of them. And they were all </div><div class="t mc35 xb7 h33 y1472 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">filled with the Holy Ghost, and began </div><div class="t m128a xb7 h33 y1f1 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to speak with other tongues, as the </div><div class="t mae2 xb7 h33 y20e ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit gave them utterance&quot; (Acts </div><div class="t m987 xb7 h33 y60e ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2:1-4). </div><div class="t m65b x15 h35 yd8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The greatest thing that ever </div><div class="t mde8 xb7 h35 y212 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hippened to the Christian church </div><div class="t m160 xb7 h35 y5eb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">happened at Pentecost. Jesus had told </div><div class="t m8ad xb7 h35 y31a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His disciples that they must wait in </div><div class="t m2e2 xb7 h35 y6ed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jerusalem until they should be endued </div><div class="t m552 xb7 h35 y19d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with power (Acts 1:4), a power to </div><div class="t m589 xb7 h35 y8e3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">witness which would accompany the </div><div class="t m8d9 xb7 h35 y155 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">outpouring of the Holy Spirit. When it </div><div class="t m1344 xb9 h35 y404 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">came, the disciples were able to </div><div class="t m84a xb9 h35 y1f9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">preach the gospel in such a way that </div><div class="t m163 xb9 h35 y9ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">everyone received the message in his </div><div class="t mfa xb9 h35 y5d4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">own language (Acts 2:6). Such a </div><div class="t m70b xb9 h35 y4cd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritual manifestation was convincing </div><div class="t m2df xb9 h35 y10 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">evidence that what was preached was </div><div class="t m130d xb9 h35 y1a4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">true. </div><div class="t m998 x27 h35 ybf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The church must always have the </div><div class="t m9ba xb9 h35 y658 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power of the Holy Spirit in order to </div><div class="t mdec xb9 h35 y91d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">carry on its witness. In the world, </div><div class="t m121 xb9 h35 ye8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">where there are so many languages </div><div class="t m119 xb9 h35 y6f3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and dialects, it is necessary to speak </div><div class="t mdd2 xb9 h35 yba0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in the language or dialect of every </div><div class="t m73e xb9 h35 y237 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nation, tribe, and people. That is why </div><div class="t m15a xb9 h35 y33f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible societies have so many Scripture </div><div class="t m289 xb9 h35 y8f1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">translations available, and missionaries </div><div class="t m19 xb9 h35 y5f0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">must learn the languages of the </div><div class="t ma99 xb9 h35 yf60 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">people to whom they go. This facility </div><div class="t m820 xb9 h35 y7b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">must be under the direction of the </div><div class="t mf58 xb9 h35 y309 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Holy Spirit if it is to accomplish </div><div class="t m80e xb9 h35 ydee ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what God has in mind, the widespread </div><div class="t mc6d x3 h35 y84 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">propagation of truth. </div><div class="t m1569 x27 h35 y85 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Unfortunately, the devil is not </div><div class="t m6b6 x3 h35 y2cd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">willing that this should happen. </div><div class="t mb3 x3 h35 y298 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">There</div><div class="t m386a x5d h35 y298 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m120 x48 h35 y298 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fore he seeks to confuse and </div><div class="t m81c x3 h35 y35d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">delay. He institutes a counterfeit  </div><div class="t m47f x1c h35 y291a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">manifestation of the use of tongues. </div><div class="t m234 x1c h35 y17e5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We note in many Christian churches </div><div class="t m6b4 x1c h35 y44e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">today an emphasis on the &quot;speaking </div><div class="t m144c x5a h35 yd18 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in tongues.&quot; But tongues in many </div><div class="t ma5 x5a h35 y5f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cases are mostly gibberish. In our </div><div class="t ma42 x1c h35 y204c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lesson today we shall try to </div><div class="t m595 x5a h35 y2af ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">differentiate between the true and </div><div class="t m10a x5a h35 yd4f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the false. The true must always be a </div><div class="t m576 x5a h35 y4fa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">characteristic of the church. The false </div><div class="t m41c x5a h35 y1034 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">must always be avoided and </div><div class="t mbc1 x5a h35 y778 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">condemned. </div><div class="t m99 x5a h33 y293 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m2c9 x5a h33 y9a ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t mbdd x86 h33 ycf8 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Speaking in Tongues </div><div class="t m1961 x4b h33 y490 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 12:28) </div><div class="t m119f x5a h33 y221 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m148b x4b h33 y221 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A False Priority </div><div class="t m6a5 x4b h33 y1e2 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 14:1) </div><div class="t m3ce x5a h33 y7a ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m1bbf x86 h33 y7a ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Testing the Spirits </div><div class="t meb7 x4b h33 y506 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 John 4:1) </div><div class="t mb06 xb0 h33 y5c8 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m830 x4b h33 y7f ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Noting the Fruits </div><div class="t m1728 x4b h33 y487 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 7:20) </div><div class="t mb06 xb0 h33 y8aa ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m12fc x4b h33 y8aa ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Deceptive Appearances </div><div class="t m1728 x4b h33 y430 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 7:15) </div><div class="t me5d xb0 h33 y117 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m449 x4b h33 y117 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Spirit-filled Life </div><div class="t m1728 x4b h33 y18c ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 3:11) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
